dc_title_s: Law Enforcement Response Districts Oneida County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data layer represents Law Enforcement response districts in Oneida County, Wisconsin in 2020. [This polygon feature class represents Emergency Service Number zones or areas that cover Oneida County. The entire county is included in one of the associated polygons.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: http://oneida.ncwrpc.info/
